# williamzade.dev

My personal developer site. A clean, responsive portfolio showcasing key projects, contact info, and dev blog entries.

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Astro or Next.js (final decision TBD)
- Styling: TailwindCSS + Custom Design
- Deployment: GitHub Pages, Vercel, or Netlify

## Features
- Project portfolio pages with write-ups and GitHub links
- Dark mode and mobile-friendly layout
- Integrated contact form

